index b5af3efcb4..b952b4c650 100644
--- a/docs/api/session.md
+++ b/docs/api/session.md
@@ -1446,6 +1446,12 @@ JavaScript in the worker global scope before the worker's main script is
 evaluated. Dedicated workers have Node.js globals only when
 `nodeIntegrationInWorker` is enabled.

+For `service-worker` contexts, scripts run in Electron's isolated
+`ShadowRealmGlobalScope` by default to preserve existing behavior. Set `target`
+to `service-worker-global-scope` to run the preload in the actual
+`ServiceWorkerGlobalScope`, where worker Web APIs such as `navigator` are
+available, or `both` to run it in both global scopes.
+
 Returns `string` - The ID of the registered preload script.

 #### `ses.unregisterPreloadScript(id)`
